      <details open><summary>Do you buy cars in Cantonment? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Yes — we buy cars, trucks, vans and SUVs in Cantonment and across north Escambia County, with <b>free towing</b>. Call {{ siteSettings.phoneNumber }} or get an offer online.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Will you come to Cantonment to pick up my car? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Yes. It's a short run north — we schedule a <b>same-day or convenient pickup</b> and tow it free. You don't have to bring it in.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Do you buy cars that don't run? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Yes — <b>running or not</b>, wrecked, flooded, or just worn out.</div></details>
      <details><summary>Can I sell without a title? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Often, yes. As a licensed Florida salvage dealer we can use a <b>Derelict Motor Vehicle Certificate</b> for older, low-value vehicles. Call and we'll tell you what applies.</div></details>
      <details><summary>How fast can you pay me? <span class="pm">+</span></summary><div class="ans">Often the <b>same day</b> — cash in hand at pickup, paperwork handled.</div></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

